IBM Garage for Cloud Developer Tools
To use the Starter Kit templates, click on the link and then the
button to create a version in your own git organization.
Then clone it onto your local machine and then use
to register it with your Jenkins server.

ibmcloud login | oc login
kubectl get pods | oc get pods
npm i -g @garage-catalyst/ibm-garage-cloud-cli
git clone <generated startkit template>
cd <generated startkit template>
code package.json ! rename your project and push changes
igc pipeline -n dev
